ard on one of Alexandria’s beaches, Halemo actually can not swim which puts him in many comedic situations.','112 minutes',1083772,'+12','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_c2b958656f6d1b33f1e75cf71c00e2f6944f325b9a72de13e9a40772829df6fb.jpg',3),('Mohammed Ali Street',2034435,'14 September 2017','Joe comes back to Egypt after a long time living abroad. As nostalgia sends him back to Mohamed Ali Street to relive his old memories, he is shocked to see what the street has become and how the belly dancers\' standards and morality have deteriorated. He saves a girl from a gang and falls for her.','80 minutes',0,NULL,'Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_9e5b4932b458872c891887dda13f4c2e61c9df23e102c323e179a8a3ae1a9baf.jpg',0),('Zay Oud Al-Kabrit',2034447,'24 August 2014','A comedic tale created by the late actor Hussein Imam to pay tribute to the stars of the Egyptian cinema in its golden age. The main story is based on mixing scenes of 21-star from black and white period with other scenes written by and starring Imam so that the final product is the rediscovering of old stars in a new context. \n\n','84 minutes',0,NULL,'No','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_17adba0cb456aefb5156c3826995541eb3cc93f3355893ef4856eb70ab3b33ef.jpg',4),('Half Dozen of Girls',2034715,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/blank_photos/75x75.jpg',0),('Soua\' Tafahom',2034735,'11 February 2015','Omar is trying to reclaim the inheritance of his father from his uncle. He uses his colleague Rauof, who turns out to be a crook and then flees to Lebanon and Omar goes to jail.  Lina the Lebanese girl falls in love with Raouf, and they agree to marry, but he escapes to Cairo.\n\n\n','120 minutes',565546,NULL,'No','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_117086716013e64e90e4f65f8279217b484dcfd47e9753d81e59eac207f1e0fa.jpg',6),('Zan',2034825,'1 January 2014','Hamad is a Saudi businessman who is desperate to have a son. After five years, his wife Laila fears