ry and migrate behind her family\'s back, but she is shocked to learn that she\'s pregnant by her boyfriend whom she left a month earlier. ','15 minutes',0,NULL,'Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_2c066e2f74104e582a5607b2435759a4b729c279d2457f105f3164e0578ed64c.jpg',0),('Something Cold',2049585,NULL,NULL,'20 minutes',0,NULL,NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_e3097d94f1020641d56f9e8502ae5ba2606453090c879e4878d550f48f841a15.jpg',0),('Red Velvet',2049586,NULL,NULL,'15 minutes',0,NULL,NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_077a94c7f15e843a6409c7eea778ad08e9c784f4c233e900f566316c0be88cb2.jpg',0),('El Badla',2049624,'20 August 2018','When two friends decide to go to a costume party, they pick police uniforms to don as their costumes, only for their old classmates to mistake them for actual policemen, which puts them in many unexpected situations. \n','96 minutes',67085009,'All Ages','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_d3be2ecb2d6318f48f93b93bf98e9ecf3c04740a801df2fc494fb8e1c4b20f4a.jpg',8),('The Secret History Of Kawthar',2049699,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_cecd20658104c36c64a50710d1606328efda5f9c8b60f3d8f4854fc135a87aaa.jpg',0),('Bani Adam',2049762,'18 August 2018','A thriller about the businessman Adam who faces criminal charges until the police enlist him for a critical mission. Will he deliver, or show an unexpected hidden side?','114 minutes',9177121,'+12','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_25bc7776321c58c1c24a3e530bcc36d0163a8bf0fa4bbf6a1998b2331754a057.jpg',7),('Feather',2049782,NULL,NULL,'10 minutes',0,NULL,NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_b415cddc16f6fb2cb45374a4f23447168d8881753009f58de277c53f3627ea20.jpg',0),('Cactus Flower',2049802,'28 January 2017','Aida, a rising actress from a rural background, finds herself overnight thrown out on the streets with her bourgeois withdrawn neighbor, Samiha. With the help of a young man named Yassin, they beg