 of bounty hunting. Their real mission is to save his kidnapped son from the hands of Franco and his ISIS gangsters after they assaulted Syrian refugees, including Yehia\'s wife, and took away the children to a district that is currently under his control.','110 minutes',18574977,'+12','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_1965fa652f9c4bcfe209dfa653859ea609d067cd84117b23a5b0b695620ba78d.jpg',6),('Mohamed Hussein',2052720,'4 June 2019','When world-renowned artist Sherif Kamal returns to Egypt after 37 years abroad, his step-daughter refuses to allow him to complete his last painting and takes revenge on him. However, she soon learns that before his death, Sherif sketched a painting on the back of Mohamed Hussein, a driver.','96 minutes',4790605,'All Ages','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_367c9541ff34d27c033b85289a7334675ca8f09dd3fbca4f7d6e31c32b469c34.jpg',6),('Lees Baghdad',2052844,'22 January 2020','In an atmosphere of suspense and excitement, Yousef, Khaled, and Nadia embark on a journey to locate the tomb of Alexander the Great, which has been sought by everyone for years.','102 minutes',33224245,'+12','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_caedcc9a050d5fd0ad6d0dcdcc205dcd8b6e3830bb83ab23bf5cd11d2cf5605f.jpg',7),('Bein Bahrain',2052991,'16 October 2018','On a visit to a suburb of Cairo, Zahraa\'s daughter has a tragic accident, and the mother tries to help the daughter overcome the adversity and continue her education. ','88 minutes',49008,'+12','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_49c7f1c74685789d31bd808d146f76e6fcdfae6f8532ac6e0aff9f331d50a4ff.jpg',6),('Manican',2053153,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_b1e3ab2fa9bdd18f77721f241bdf1cf931604291fa1fe98a0cd567345621130b.jpg',0),('Yom W Leila',2053246,'6 January 2020','The story revolves around a policeman who\'s investigating some social issues, especially those related to the crises of the poor inside the Mawlid of Al-Sayeda Zain