ber 2019','When a famous singer is hired to perform in the closing ceremony of the Arabic Music Festival in Marrakesh, he soon finds himself falling victim to the machinations of a smuggler, who makes use of the singer\'s fame to smuggle a papyrus, which hails from the Akhenaten era, from Morocco to Europe.','120 minutes',0,'All Ages','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_04b4fc2b74e4f427cb932694865d5e5d47d484765ff1ebce1cafed460582901f.jpg',5),('Al-Felos',2055129,'24 December 2019','Sief is a conman who is hired by the beautiful rich woman, Hala, to help her get her money back from another conman. Their relationship gets them entangled in a web of deceit as they start questioning their stances regarding love, friendship, and the meaning of life. \n','118 minutes',47851475,'All Ages','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_7d4357267d6502afd425a2cda0302c9efd3ca74d989323c7a1c4cc16af34aa5c.jpg',7),('Mako',2055208,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_87cdecb08722079acef66e09fe5ab9e185b88171cfb98fb1eda6f9bbb572a179.jpg',0),('Aeaza Alwalad',2055450,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'All Ages',NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_0e3b2045260da502760436b03fad9ec23bdbd5f500fbc43d5fcd1eaa75c8bb16.jpg',7),('Sab\'e Alboromba',2055503,'4 June 2019','Omar marries Nesma despite her father\'s objection. After the wedding ceremony, they\'re attacked by unknown men. During her escape, Nesma is injured.  Awakening from a coma, she refuses to see Omar because she doesn\'t feel safe with him. He goes to a psychiatrist to help him solve the problem. \n','92 minutes',35082656,'All Ages','Yes','https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_dc6fb1590d21995a851a46793ceab4bff4bb296eef5915c1e14de73b230e1213.jpg',7),('Plastic',2055531,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,'https://media.elcinema.com/uploads/_75x75_3cbf7a79e8640c915b1438e6a08efc9e952590f48fd74aeb3f919080f17c896c.jpg',6),('The Demon',2055843,'16 February 2019','Omar is a timid young man who catches 